text.tspan: D. E. Shaw India Pvt. Ltd.

flowRoot.flowPara: The Design and User Experience team handles the visual design, interaction design and technical writing needs of D. E. Shaw & Co.’s software products. My role in the team is that of an interaction designer anddevelopment consultant on one side and a team manager, administrator and design evangelist on theother. As a manager, I am responsible for resource allocation, expectation management, projectplanning, status reporting and performance appraisals. An important part of the role is to marketthe team and ensure that the work-slate is always full. I make sure that the quality of deliverablesis high and that we always bring something new to the table, delivering more and better than ourclients expect. When I started on this team, we did only image prototypes. The team now delivers high fidelityHTML mockups for all its projects and is the first destination for anyone who wants expert HTML5,CSS3 and jQuery advice. Many years of experience as a UI developer have helped me ensure thatthe bar is set high. Projects I have worked on in the capacity of an interaction designer and development consultantinclude an in-house recruitment management system, the firm’s performance appraisal system, anaudit confirms engine, a tracker for month-end financial reports and a firm-wide application forstatus reporting, resource allocation and roadmap tracking.
